name: Robert L. WOODARD, Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS, Philadelphia County, Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 17th day of October, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief and Application for Immediate Hearing are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
